dct_title_s: Ymēttos / Road Ekdoseis A.E. = Mt. Hymettus : outdoor activities map / Road Editions S.A.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Text, color illustrations, tables of caves showing latitude, longitude, and altitude, and 2 maps of part of Mt. Hymettus. Panel title. On verso: text, color illustrations, tables of caves showing latitude, longitude, and elevation. 2 maps, scale 1:10,000, showing location of rock climbing fields, caves and monasteries located in Mt. Hymettus.
